  "prompt": "Where can I learn Tai-Chi in Bangalore?",
  "response": "In Bangalore, there are several places where you can learn Tai Chi. Consider the following options:\n\n1. **Tai Chi Classes at Gyms or Fitness Studios**: Many gyms and fitness studios offer Tai Chi classes as part of their group classes. Check local studios for schedules.\n\n2. **Tai Chi Schools or Martial Arts Centers**: Look for schools that specialize in martial arts or traditional Chinese practices. Some might offer dedicated Tai Chi programs.\n\n3. **Community Centers**: Some community centers or cultural organizations may host Tai Chi classes. These classes may cater to all skill levels.\n\n4. **Yoga Studios**: A number of yoga studios incorporate Tai Chi into their offerings or might have instructors who can teach it.\n\n5. **Online Platforms**: If in-person options are limited, consider online classes or tutorials. Websites and apps may offer structured programs.\n\n6. **Local Meetups**: Platforms like Meetup.com may have Tai Chi groups that practice in parks or community spaces.\n\nConsider reaching out to local instructors, checking reviews, or visiting classes to find the best fit for you.",
